casebody.data:
The State ex rel. Bragg, Appellant, v. Custodian of Records, Cuyahoga County, Appellee.

[Cite as State ex rel. Bragg v. Custodian of Records, Cuyahoga Cty. (1992), 65 Ohio St.3d 319.]

*320(No. 92-1451 — Submitted October 13, 1992 — Decided December 14, 1992.) John T Bragg, pro se. Danny R. Williams, Director of Law, and Pamela A. Pfleger Walker, Assistant Director of Law, for appellee.

The judgment of the court of appeals is affirmed.

Moyer, C.J., Sweeney, Holmes, Douglas, Wright, H. Brown and Resnick, JJ., concur.
